							<a href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AWhat’s Next for Deep-Sea Mining?%0D%0AWith mining applications on the horizon, the International Seabed Authority’s crucial Mining Code is still far from finished.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/whats-next-for-deep-sea-mining/" title="Share by Email" target="_blank">
